<title>ạskn fy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạskn fy yạ rby wạgẖfr ly ḍʿf
 qlby
 wạsndny yạ ḥbyby fy dẖly wkl tʿby
 2- ạrsẖdny fy ạldrwb ạḥmyny fy ạlṭryq
 sạʿdny ʿly̱ ạlwjwd bḥb byk ylyq
 3- ạdkẖl fy ạlạ̉mạn ạskb ly ạlḥnạn
 ạrwyny mn nbʿ ḥbk rạfqny ṭwl ạlzmạn
 4- ḥbyby lys swạk nfsy tṭlb rḍạk
 dʿny ạ̉srʿ ạ̹lyk lạ̉ḥyạ fy smạk
 5- lạ tnsa wʿdk yạ rby wạnqsẖny fy ydyk
 ky yfrḥ bk qlby wnfsy tsrʿ ạ̹lyk</lyrics>
</song>